OL,7,FLindsay MacCallum, 61, admitted to
OL,8,Fstealing the money from The Rainbow
OL,9,FValley Foundation between February
OL,10,F2013 and November 2021. She also
OL,11,Fembezzled more than #9,500 from the
OL,12,FAnthony Nolan Trust.
OL,14,FThe Rainbow Valley Foundation was
OL,15,Fjointly set up by MacCallum and her
OL,16,Fbest friend Angela MacVicar, who lost
OL,17,Fher daughter Johanna to leukaemia in
OL,18,F2005 aged 27. It was aimed at helping
OL,19,Fthose facing the disease, and their
OL,20,Ffamilies.
