OL,7,FOn Tuesday a judge said she had
OL,8,Fbrought "devastation" to those who
OL,9,Ftrusted her.
OL,11,FMs MacVicar said of her friend: "I
OL,12,Floved her and I trusted her, and she
OL,13,Fwas in a position of trust."
OL,15,F"I was bereft when I found out," Ms
OL,16,FMacVicar added. "She fooled everybody."
