OL,7,FSpeaking after the sentencing, Ms
OL,8,FMacVicar added: "She had a few
OL,9,Fapologies, and they were to her
OL,10,Ffamily, there was no mention of what
OL,11,Fshe's done to our family and my
OL,12,Fdaughter's name and I feel she's sorry
OL,13,Fshe was caught."
OL,15,F"The ripple effect of hurt caused by
OL,16,FLindsay MacCallum runs deep. I ask
OL,17,Fpeople to remember this was one
OL,18,Fperson, and one person alone, who
OL,19,Fbreached the position of trust that
OL,20,Fwas bestowed upon her."
