OL,7,FMacCallum set up a bank account to
OL,8,Freceive donations for the charity, and
OL,9,Farranged for them to be routed through
OL,10,Fa bank account she had access to in
OL,11,Fher official capacity.
OL,13,FShe would then transfer the money to
OL,14,Fher personal bank accounts or use it
OL,15,Fto pay for her own expenses.
OL,17,FMacCallum told the court she intended
OL,18,Fto pay all the money back.
